  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e3d46142-85be-45f5-b4c2-11442a17348e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2f6cdfd2-b613-485f-8c91-4504eb9173f8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9955a656-17b0-4cc4-b1bd-7b32731329af\"><b>안녕하세요 사당로 한의원 이수한의원입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-e3d46142-85be-45f5-b4c2-11442a17348e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8297c739-8570-433c-8d02-721a28c15ca5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"11\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_11.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-162ec356-78fc-4b43-a6e8-d6bbdc335495\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8f7282fb-b7fc-4b14-971c-7f687acf5d15\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3aca8543-c636-445c-9ec9-2600f975f55c\"><b>속이 더부룩하고 소화가 잘 안 되는 이유… </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a23565bf-f0af-4711-94bc-6c5b3ee326b7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4d3551e7-e229-4f4f-ae29-1a6e8fc4d401\"><b>혹시 식습관 때문일까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6ef645a5-e7d3-43cb-b6e4-044f594a4fad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9c9f4c8f-a68a-421c-96aa-834adb19d335\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-68b3665e-c9a2-4a08-a357-9ec36a364bea\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5ec34947-f9ab-4cf5-b5b7-879050406857\">밥을 먹고 난 뒤 속이 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a62466c7-b423-48f9-9993-3af382ab4f58\"><b>더부룩하고 답답한 경험</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cbecb6ae-2e47-4479-ada3-1b2540048d46\">을 자주 하시나요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-edea6bc8-a49d-4288-961d-cbc3e37e9f72\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a226e991-d708-4902-9f2e-d71ad8059656\">소화불량은 단순한 불편감을 넘어, 반복되면 위 건강을 해치고 만성 질환으로 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9b43f33e-f349-41b6-8004-fc34b7768158\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b1443653-7851-4d34-925d-13138d5abdca\">이어질 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a9436bd3-30ca-4781-873e-a48437a160c5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7dedf1b2-ccb0-44fd-bbee-bdc5c257befa\">오늘은 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-edccae72-27a6-4489-8810-56d002088751\"><b>소화불량의 원인과 위 건강을 지키는 생활습관</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-02bd1555-33ed-4734-99a0-5af12697db0a\">에 대해 알아보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-162ec356-78fc-4b43-a6e8-d6bbdc335495\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-d2fc570d-75d0-4bad-87e9-3a48c0b97c49\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7ce00f3d-cad8-4e38-b757-95ce119fb99d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7ce00f3d-cad8-4e38-b757-95ce119fb99d\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5364a72010a5876d.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5364a72010a5876d.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5364a72010a5876d.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-7ce00f3d-cad8-4e38-b757-95ce119fb99d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-b4dc0964-a086-4d46-b8b3-6f1d07e63712\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6adf0a20-d7eb-4b38-93c8-8608b3af2f70\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-285f2d20-3d55-4a7b-ace7-a755dd6bb2f8\"><b>소화불량이 생기는 대표적인 원인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6ca40f09-c254-4c37-911a-f923d864d497\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b1ef55c0-9f32-4b37-86f5-d5497bf22132\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-84d59c31-197e-493f-be22-f826801bc5e0\">소화불량은 크게 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7f9c4f81-3f64-4a5d-afe3-61396b565edb\"><b>기능성 소화불량</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-92981d21-9217-4e28-873e-7ef950127643\">과 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1c422455-4455-450a-941a-fff6bb9c8196\"><b>기질적 소화불량</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-27f94217-96f7-4ca8-a1c0-4a215f223ada\">으로 나눌 수 있습니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9f643056-d9cd-4634-9bab-8faee35f184b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-855ae8f3-f7f0-478c-868a-ff434a128ccc\"><b>식습관 문제</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-58ceb4a3-ebf0-439e-a569-60d9aa3a44f9\">: 빨리 먹기, 과식, 늦은 밤 야식, 기름진 음식</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1ee9379d-764e-4746-b84c-b9e39b14dadc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7b2fff39-1165-4bf2-8fbc-cc74c3ce8eb5\"><b>스트레스와 불규칙한 생활</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4cfcdbc9-1a51-4465-85a2-4d93582287ad\">: 위 운동 저하, 위산 분비 불균형 유발</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e8c72610-a352-4092-8f51-644cd29f173f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-931c36f7-f3a2-410e-bb52-312b80e0c797\"><b>기질적 요인</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5330a309-a941-4ecb-add8-13e3f358acd0\">: 위염, 역류성 식도염, 위궤양 등 질환 동반</span></p></li></ul><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a19efb71-9eb8-42c0-86ee-11b1b805d54a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1a3f197c-5e7c-4471-acc6-0f865aa85dff\">한의학에서는 위장이 약해져 기혈 순환이 원활하지 못하거나 </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-63c5c76b-6da0-47d8-8c3d-cf45b5892b05\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5cbb9e48-f933-4260-ac84-1c5d556ace97\">담적(노폐물·독소 축적)이 생겨 위 기능이 떨어지는 것으로 봅니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-6ca40f09-c254-4c37-911a-f923d864d497\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-66f1fedb-e2c2-408f-a91e-e4e2906f4d79\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-512ca921-bdb3-4511-b6bc-e4262503e08d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-59e32a7d-9368-4a3d-b05c-b81d58645491\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e26107da-bf8a-425e-b884-d04ee3b9820c\"><b> </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0108086f-667a-449f-99bb-d9010290789c\"><b>속이 안 좋을 때 고기를 피해야 하는 이유</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9982f9fe-1065-405e-89ca-930f6cf2bded\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-43742c54-76f2-4bae-8b52-76f762efcc5f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2155519b-5633-468c-83b5-45c3b5619dcb\">위가 약해졌을 때 고기를 많이 먹으면 소화 효소 분비가 원활하지 않아 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ae4a83f9-ca23-441b-8afd-9b16da195f2b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9e75b583-639a-4a08-9f76-17ae0027cc92\"><b>부패·발효 과정이 길어지고, 가스와 더부룩함</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fd4211e1-bde1-4f9f-a0ad-c05b087d1519\">을 악화시킵니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-181fe594-a8ef-4baa-bb48-4b019c94f91e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e7b16594-5903-4a64-90d4-0ccd1776d3c5\">특히 기름지고 자극적인 육류는 위 점막에 부담을 주어 위산 역류나 소화 장애를 유발할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-9982f9fe-1065-405e-89ca-930f6cf2bded\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-d5bed34e-57ec-4eae-9fb3-20ab7799a51b\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-d95469e7-55dc-4ad9-8f2d-3e454d537a5a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d61a6722-9a11-4415-b5e3-1480045d28f0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bb9da133-b7d8-409f-b956-768ba93461ae\"><b> </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-623f246e-aff6-462e-9e02-f5ee165aa006\"><b>위 건강을 지키는 올바른 식사 습관</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ea2dd62f-4a9c-4a41-a7f4-3cd180b5d945\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-84b45b4a-5c2b-4ab4-b9eb-10a50f929b08\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-349ab5ce-a463-4fa8-a249-068d53e3753d\">작은 습관의 변화가 위 건강을 크게 바꿀 수 있습니다.</span></p><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4fab75c5-bbd1-4e35-955f-fdb278400e3d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b0c32cb6-542f-4731-9d91-90e578a7b370\"><b>20번 이상 꼭꼭 씹기</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5e2eedd6-0f00-4e4b-a8d3-d6e66e6139fb\">: 위의 부담을 줄이고 소화 효소 분비 촉진</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eababa9e-97dc-4183-9d8d-29b6a30e6244\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ae5e73fe-729a-40b3-b974-9740a5b026fd\"><b>규칙적인 식사 시간</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-453ee146-cc10-4362-a6a0-22341a2d691a\">: 위 운동 리듬을 일정하게 유지</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3052ef88-627a-475b-bfa3-32a9c01b29f5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-657522af-8523-453b-86c0-c8a01ea9ccba\"><b>과식·폭식 피하기</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ffbd5e28-469e-4ac8-b32c-0c796a0ebdfd\">: 위에 과부하 방지</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-97772898-b7a9-4a5e-a63d-a06b1d5e5a3d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-538c33e3-bf53-489b-8ac1-7ca575d0f6ff\"><b>늦은 야식 줄이기</b></span><span style=\"\" cl