mponent-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a88c4bbc-9f80-45d2-a58b-e792e472220f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9bfca0e5-afe1-48c1-9433-c2814ff75fd8\"><b>피해야 할 음식</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-585e7d6a-e602-4b8b-898d-98c1be27850b\">: 기름진 튀김, 맵고 짠 음식, 과도한 카페인·술</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ca61092e-b90d-41c7-a632-29769700941b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f8a62b57-8514-4c70-b5ba-8d3889b3d350\"><b>좋은 음식</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3a447f05-9880-4918-84f5-46380f900ccd\">: 부드러운 죽, 채소·과일, 소화 잘 되는 단백질(두부, 흰살 생선 등)</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-debb5000-0337-4d0d-9a43-adcc6f4918a1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a474e0c9-06f7-4dea-868e-691d10580fc9\"><b>생활 관리</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ee1e3e25-cf8e-487f-9a18-f8728a7ee863\">: 스트레스 완화, 충분한 수면, 적당한 운동</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-4c4540ed-854e-4978-8d0b-02ce946573b9\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-4a6825f4-010d-4746-8769-d421bfbecbb2\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-c